name: Marquel Martin

social_posts.post_text:
It’s been written #Maktub. 

Welcome to @3point0labs: an all-in-one advisory company that meets at the cross-section of web3, sports & innovation.

Last week was by FAR the best educational experience of my life! 🙏🏾Surrounded by some of the best and brightest minds across entertainment, media and sports, I’m just humbled and incredibly blessed to have been a part of the @harvardhbs BEMS Program. The opportunity to learn business from one of the best professors in the entire world in @anitaelberse, is something I’ll cherish forever and apply the strategies and learnings to @3point0labs to the best of my abilities. To miss Anita and my classmates, I luv y’all. Thank you for inspiring me to be the best version of myself. I wish you all the best in your endeavors. I’m here to help and know that you have a friend for life. See you soon ✌🏾🤓#BEMS2023 #Maktub 💫
#fbf Take me back to that higher learning, because I’m more confident than ever in my abilities. Your boy is getting smarter and smarter s/o @harvardhbs @anitaelberse 😄😎📚
The boy has Got his OWN music video and it’s LEGENDARY 🔥♟️.
“I mean the man has got his own statue!” ♟️

Through all the hate, through all the pain, through all the slander, through all the threats, through all the deceit. I (We) persevered…we did it. I’m beyond grateful. So this fight week…I just smile. Thank you to all of the real ones who’ve supported me. 🙏🏾God is great. #Maktub

This video was Seven years ago (October 18, 2016) after getting laid off with a lot of my colleagues when WME purchased UFC for $4 Billion… listen to what I said- “God has some great things planned for me…” #Maktub 💫
Marquel Martin talks about the magnitude of Fury vs. Ngannou 👀 #TheMMAHour
“The fondest memories are made when gathered around the table.” #History #Maktub
Happy Birthday to my best friend and the BEST human being I know. 💜 🫵👁️🔫4️⃣🫵
SOME of this amazing 2023. I did it my way. (Which is trust God)♟️ To God be the Glory. Happy New Year everyone! God Bless. …See you at work.🙏🏾#Maktub
